text: Input/Output Data The SQS Forwarding Agent receives UDRs of type SqsForwarderCycleUDR and forwards them as messages to Amazon SQS. MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop | MIM . Publishes The SQS Forwarding Agent does not publish any MIMs. Accesses The SQS Forwarding Agent does not access any MIM parameters.
